{"tid":1045133,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"畢業後，我成為冥婚證婚人","createTime":"2019-03-03T11:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T12:26:25.000Z","uid":120629,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"61e92a05b7510ebcc4c912728268a29e2cc8e407","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"我是成器，一個專為亡者冥婚的人。<br />\n<br />\n二十三歲大學畢業，有的同學考督察，有的同學當老師，有的同學投身金融，只有我，承繼祖業。<br />\n<br />\n我想當冥婚師嗎?<br />\n<br />\n人所追求的不是一份理想的工作，而是一份自己不太抗拒的工作。<br />\n<br />\n我不抗拒當冥婚師。"},{"pid":"d2a49c23d5fdd3343dd0dbed3bf9d023bc99dd07","tid":1045133,"uid":226216,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"咁我拜一拜先<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/195225_70c64c8ebe35f109efb5a6c7a8e3f397.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F195225_70c64c8ebe35f109efb5a6c7a8e3f397.gif&h=f58233a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a98c784655bc587d50b078467df6fc824112db2","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"「成器，明天的案件有點複雜，萬一亡者家屬找你麻煩，你要隨機應變，不能自亂陣腳。」爺爺拄著拐杖，步履蹣跚地往我身旁坐下。<br />\n<br />\n從出世那天，只有爺爺照顧我，我的回憶沒有丁點兒關於父母的片段，他似是一個不存在的人物。<br />\n<br />\n筆家從未出現任何一位女性，爺爺對此絕口不提，我的母親是誰?我有母親嗎?兒時的我總對家中狀況提出種種疑問，卻得不到答案。<br />\n<br />\n沒有父母的家庭又如何?我沒有半點悲傷。<br />\n<br />\n人會因為得不到而悲傷，會因為失去而悲傷﹔我並非得不到父母，也不是失去了父母，悲傷不會在我心房油然而生。<br />\n<br />\n我的生活，已排除了父母二字。"},{"pid":"3b4bd387c4c8ad0831f987bdaa53c01863167970","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"「他是成家的冥婚師，你和欣宜的婚禮將由他主持。」陳老先生把我介紹給冥婚的男主角，他的兒子陳家健認識。<br />\n<br />\n陳老先生為兒子安排婚禮大大小小的細節，一直以來關於冥婚事宜也是由他直接和我們溝通，直至婚禮當天我才第一天看見阿健。<br />\n<br />\n阿健的面容略帶憔悴，身穿全白西裝的他對我微微點頭，我們的交集只限於此。<br />\n<br />\n冥婚會場定於殯儀館，出殯與婚禮二合為一能方便各方親友，亦能展現出生者對亡者的重視，就算陰陽相隔也不改二人的愛情。"},{"pid":"17b6c2bd29119ac4bee72a15343a6b27baa6e8bb","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"愛情不需要天荒地老，年期亦不需一萬年，從實際的角度出發，用一輩子的行動去證明對另一半的愛情。<br />\n<br />\n冥婚，除了為亡者相互婚配外，也能為生死相隔的情侶給予對方一個名份。<br />\n<br />\n請不要以為冥婚只是口頭承諾，這是一場憑著自己的良心所締結的婚姻。<br />\n<br />\n「各位來賓請盡快就坐，並把所有電子產品轉為靜音模式，以免妨礙婚禮進行。」我清清嗓門，向在場賓客義正詞嚴地說道。<br />\n<br />\n畢竟香港人對儀式不太重視，無論是婚禮還是葬禮，也缺少應有的尊重。<br />\n<br />\n他們不只是不尊重主人家，也是不尊重自己。"},{"pid":"6da9a0351625252ac5aa467d6deae74be44736f7","tid":1045133,"uid":155180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推一推"},{"pid":"5bee01188b19b718b79d32b8792b101cd32235b1","tid":1045133,"uid":208499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150eef8384aa4834c7ba08eea64d4636d09c034b","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"是日婚禮意義異常重要，這天是我第一次獨自主持冥婚儀式，我懷著戰戰兢兢的心情站在靈堂中央。<br />\n<br />\n「現在婚禮正式開始，有請新郎進場。」<br />\n<br />\n「假如，在座各位失去生命之中的唯一，你們會怎樣做?」我凝視眾人，有人以衛生紙拭淚，有人垂下頭讓淚水點點滴在大腿，有人輕輕搭著另一半的肩膀給予安慰。<br />\n<br />\n「其實，當你真正愛一個人，無論他的軀體在哪，你也會用盡方法去說服自己，認為他一直在你身旁。」"},{"pid":"a18e961a8496a26edfd717bd7664b7b18576c161","tid":1045133,"uid":77388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:20:32.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e048d7564f404029017cfabff7112d22bf93b04","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:30:06.000Z","msg":"「因為你愛他，你會為他找不同的藉口，用盡一切方法也要跟他在一起，永遠也不想與他分離。」<br />\n<br />\n「有人會認為枕邊人死後會化成蝴蝶彌留縈繞於愛人身邊，也有人相信愛侶會係遙遠既天邊默默守護自己。一切的推測都源自於人對離別的抗拒。」<br />\n<br />\n「其實，你們的愛侶一直都留係自己的身旁，他們欠的只是一個名份，一個被肯定的名份。」<br />\n<br />\n婚禮現場播放著欣宜生前與阿健的片段，他充滿笑容，把女朋友緊緊抱在懷裡。"},{"pid":"ce7f6ba75f88d4bfc46f627d093715b4a085e6ba","tid":1045133,"uid":240278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:37:07.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b00847d83c2f708adb3c2f72a760382815874b0","tid":1045133,"uid":212345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"重製？之前好似有個差唔多的故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91685705ead5ff4a814c76101cd7de8a6ab5ca46","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b00847d83c2f708adb3c2f72a760382815874b0","tid":1045133,"uid":212345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"重製？之前好似有個差唔多的故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:03:13.000Z","msg":"冇錯，換左個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f4f448ac2728d3238b7a5c7dde6c7e2178fd7e","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"如果支持就請留個正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d3b40b3134c81417a64fc9899dc886597c1491","tid":1045133,"uid":12494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f4f448ac2728d3238b7a5c7dde6c7e2178fd7e","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"如果支持就請留個正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:49:54.000Z","msg":"正皮"},{"pid":"f4d6515044193fe8377c0dd8e0880849d4f60f04","tid":1045133,"uid":212345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f4f448ac2728d3238b7a5c7dde6c7e2178fd7e","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"如果支持就請留個正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />皮"},{"pid":"dc2bbf39c20e683c6b98a11160681c0fa0c19516","tid":1045133,"uid":235477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7f40d39d3a26bf049d2e4f008202968357ab2dc3","tid":1045133,"uid":219084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:03:59.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"16fe832f866fd9d22eb480df4a7f0745136f2310","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T19:35:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"faf80ac1ed274bae1431c54fe4f6669834203e0d","tid":1045133,"uid":1517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:02:19.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db706b536511d6ebac09089963a7d11ebfc3dae2","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T22:24:05.000Z","msg":"晏d出"},{"pid":"fc41136f0efbe116942cf5cf896ecc96c1cd7a88","tid":1045133,"uid":174539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T03:54:23.000Z","msg":"點解我要咁早入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736c04d182e3a970d6ee223ea139dee1c08ce74c","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:13:27.000Z","msg":"第一段是兩人高中的回憶，穿著校服坐在天台上吹吹風，兩人肩靠著肩，這一幕被他們的好朋友記錄下來。畢業旅行，兩人站在九份的路軌上放天燈，天燈寫下「考上大學，永遠在一起。」<br />\n<br />\n只是單純地盼望待在一起，只是單純地渴望考上大學，中學生的人生只有一條路或是簡單的分岔路，讀書或是不讀書，考上或是考不上大學。<br />\n<br />\n第二段是兩人大學的回憶，穿著同樣的迎新營衣服，一起當新生又一起當上組爸媽，兩人面貼面，嘴巴對著嘴巴，背後一大群新生露出天新無邪的笑容，做出各式各樣的動作，任憑同學如何出眾也不及阿健與欣宜的愛。<br />\n<br />\n阿健背著欣宜站在南怡島的雪地上自轉，動作雖然笨拙又帶點滑稽，影片中的韓國人不時對他們投以嘲笑目光，青春就是瘋狂的。<br />\n<br />\n第三段是兩人大學畢業的回憶，站在林蔭大道的他們穿上學士袍與雙方親友合照，阿健把百變小櫻抱在懷裡，欣宜手中的則是keroro軍曹。他們把畢業帽拋往天空，眼神充滿對未來的期盼。<br />\n<br />\n最後&hellip;..這就是最後的片段，大學畢業是他們最後的片段。<br />\n<br />\n難道畢業後就沒有值得回憶的片段嗎?畢竟畢業至今兩年時間，七百多天的時間能發生很多事，能讓一個兩個孩子手挽著手步入人生另一個階段，能讓孩子從娘胎變成呱呱落地的嬰兒。"},{"pid":"00ae204f199b8e572b73b3618d1b7d0b415a5939","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"阿健沒有像電影中的男主角哭成淚人，但昏深的燈光下仍可隱約看見一顆接一顆淚珠盈滿眼眶，劃過面龐。<br />\n<br />\n「各位來賓，在座各位有一對新人的父母、親友與同學，或多或少在他們的生活中佔據一段回憶，不管前路如何，阿健的選擇就是與欣宜一起度過往後的日子。」<br />\n<br />\n燈光由暗轉亮，阿健的輪廓與面部微表情漸漸變得清楚易見。<br />\n<br />\n他用手帕輕輕拭去眼眶與臉上的淚痕，眼珠轉向上方，仿佛沒有面對來賓的勇氣，悲傷之下，他顯然失去前行的動力。<br />\n<br />\n「現在，有請新郎為大家講幾句說話。」我退後數步，讓出中間的位置。"},{"pid":"c962368a393be1a5b0f8f5861840f9939eaca5fa","tid":1045133,"uid":86684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:49:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb0b9ff610edced5335d1126f45012919d012e92","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"acff256def243704a4b05b8e0e35686c2742d065","tid":1045133,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"仆街喊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067734a946b01021d56acb7171dd9e294b056b44","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acff256def243704a4b05b8e0e35686c2742d065","tid":1045133,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"仆街喊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861ed8b284963c259dbb3aa40ede6dbdb5bea243","tid":1045133,"uid":171139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20150726/s00009/1437895441533SF_D0EC4D6B72D174FCDA04375F8E7B5D56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20150726%2Fs00009%2F1437895441533SF_D0EC4D6B72D174FCDA04375F8E7B5D56.jpg&h=e4ce33d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae28324aa40730ad887a222480c2f5c52aaaea71","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"861ed8b284963c259dbb3aa40ede6dbdb5bea243","tid":1045133,"uid":171139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20150726/s00009/1437895441533SF_D0EC4D6B72D174FCDA04375F8E7B5D56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20150726%2Fs00009%2F1437895441533SF_D0EC4D6B72D174FCDA04375F8E7B5D56.jpg&h=e4ce33d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T22:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正"},{"pid":"8d9d3b2afc132fba75a480d7e514037d03be0457","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T23:22:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4400b7d960bfebeae22980572b96046059ce7b92","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:44:50.000Z","msg":"「各位賓客，請容許我先說幾句話。」一位中年婦人從第一排的座位站起身，她穿著一整套樸素的黑色長裙，由身旁的男伴攙扶，走到台前。<br />\n<br />\n「我們是欣宜的父母，她臨終前曾經拍下一段影片，假如自己真的不幸離世，就要我們在出殯那天公開影片。就算是欣宜對大家的最後遺言。」中年婦人從手提包拿出usb手指，示意工作人員播放。<br />\n<br />\n不得不承認在我的算盤當中未有推算出這一幕情景。<br />\n<br />\n「人生總不能永遠按照你所預料的前行，人總要預上幾次意外，碰幾次壁才能成長。」還記得爺爺在我第一次陪伴他當冥婚師前的告誡。"},{"pid":"3285bb01df58cbe7cdd9045f196bbd963ebe73aa","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"不要以為人生總按照軌道前行，我們必須學懂應對所以意料之外的特發事情，做好一切接受失敗的準備。<br />\n<br />\n影片長約三分鐘，沒有背景音樂與舊照片作為鋪陳，只看見欣宜表露出憔悴的面容，勉強坐直身子依靠在床頭貼近牆壁的一邊。<br />\n<br />\n「各位賓友，首先感謝你們出席我的喪禮。這樣說雖然很奇怪，那有一個在生的人會預先感謝其他人出席自己的喪禮?可是命裡有時終需有，沒人比我更清楚自己還有多久的時間。」欣宜臉上掛著苦笑。<br />\n<br />\n阿健咬著唇，屏氣凝神地看著影片裡的欣宜，他對眼前發生的一切似是一無所知。<br />\n<br />\n「如果，阿健真的履行對我的承諾會迎娶我，那就請在座各位見證我的意願。」<br />\n<br />\n「我鄧欣宜不會嫁給程永健作為他的妻子。應該說此時此刻，我還不上決定。」欣宜隨著把無名指上的婚戒脫下。"},{"pid":"ebf9bc4c3a14fe9ade5fa7226016866661252bdd","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:52:28.000Z","msg":"賓客紛紛竊竊私語，交頭接耳，對欣宜的影片和阿健投以奇怪的目光。<br />\n<br />\n反倒是阿健一言不發地盯著欣宜，亦沒有情緒波動，一切感情只以眼淚作結。<br />\n<br />\n「阿健，還記得當初我教你英文的情境嗎?任我如何教你，你也難以記下complex sentence，這是中一、二學生應該要學懂的內容，可是作為一個中五學生，你還是搞不清當中的關係。」欣宜蒼白的面容勉強擠出微笑。"},{"pid":"b6d565158f5df734b002569f8cf07625f1a7fc27","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"「你漫不經心對我講，因為英文不像數學那樣有特定的規律，任何事情也有法則，若不能闡明清楚，你就不能理解。」<br />\n<br />\n「人的感情不會永遠只有一種，感到高興的同時也會感到有些無趣，覺得麻煩時會感到一點快樂，是很複雜的，人生不像數學那般只有單純的法則。」<br />\n<br />\n「你的人生或許像數學一樣，用不同的方法尋找一個答案。可是我的人生就像英文一樣，只為用不同的方法表達不同的意思與情感。」<br />\n<br />\n「我與你相處十個年頭，經歷中學、大學還有畢業後的時光。時間可以加深一個人對另一個人的認識與了解，可是時間也可以改變一個人的性格與習慣，或許我們之間不斷努力認識與了解對方的同時，時光也悄悄地與我們競賽，把我們改變。」<br />\n<br />\n「要不要嫁給你，我不能給你一個答案。跟你一起的時光有苦有甜，有笑有淚，與其浪費時間做一條永遠找不到答案的數學題，倒不如把精力花在另一道能找到答案的題目。」<br />\n<br />\n影片完結，欣宜最後的答案是未能決定會否嫁給阿健。"},{"pid":"a5a1a89d4dcdfb57f9fd17969cea9936b9c00045","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1025353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1025353/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"33f29ec093fccdbc39c902b9761f8517a4c96a7d","tid":1045133,"uid":138482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又出多次"},{"pid":"5a36b26ac8ff09c368c028d67ecff19b09915c75","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33f29ec093fccdbc39c902b9761f8517a4c96a7d","tid":1045133,"uid":138482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又出多次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3604a4c50e679a123e3f605fc88a5d888c70d5","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:08:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d1f03eeb772c4e3e9a0e9af6826cd044a03229f4","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5a6b2cac65f26a225ae947bb7b7f2b5911bdefff","tid":1045133,"uid":208837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"live"},{"pid":"df7dc3a3e43bd0d5064850a073e5ca059f76c721","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a6b2cac65f26a225ae947bb7b7f2b5911bdefff","tid":1045133,"uid":208837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"live"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66bb5b4d97c49984dea8eb4cdc8657f4d7fdf4d","tid":1045133,"uid":208837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df7dc3a3e43bd0d5064850a073e5ca059f76c721","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a6b2cac65f26a225ae947bb7b7f2b5911bdefff","tid":1045133,"uid":208837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"live"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"文呢樓主<br />\n好似幾好睇<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"f6f889fcb5296bdd5d172733e96b94807623f908","tid":1045133,"uid":147079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42172097b11fc448e38e63d754085f0d15a2c88a","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"阿健父親向我報以凌厲的眼神，暗示我該做一些事情。可是他的眼神不太友善，我不理解眼神背後的意思。<br />\n<br />\n「各位親友，欣宜是在意識不清醒之下才講出影片中的說話，大家一直知道阿健與欣宜是真心相愛的!或許在臨終前的一刻，她已經改變心意，只是來不及跟阿健說。」阿健的父親趕忙打圓場，說到最後更狠狠地瞪了欣宜家人一下。<br />\n<br />\n「就讓我去問問欣宜的意見。」語出，換來整個靈堂的一片沉默，來賓四目交投。<br />\n<br />\n冥婚在不少人心目中是一場猴子戲，就像冥婚人假借亡者與在世的人互動。所謂借則有，不信則無，眾人懷疑是因為他們不相信，而不是冥婚是虛假。<br />\n<br />\n冥婚是真實的事實是永恆不變，一切在乎觀點與角度。<br />\n<br />\n「假如你們把冥婚當作一場戲，恕我難以待下去。如果你們相信冥婚是要經過兩人的同意，請讓我找欣宜問她的意見。」我的情緒有點意料之外的波動。"},{"pid":"41f8d70b411012fed10fc1c75205d4d63b1ad83f","tid":1045133,"uid":6491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"More"},{"pid":"c9497b05dce26c2d7a7da41881d54a65b6632cb3","tid":1045133,"uid":223672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"160d9adc38176bf663ff5aab3732610032d0a536","tid":1045133,"uid":1517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e6fb6df2421bfef8b07be64a5ba837ac398613","tid":1045133,"uid":40836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T00:15:46.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"85ce127292a10a935649f524517c951ae3b1ff14","tid":1045133,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:25:27.000Z","msg":"晚上再出，感謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}